import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], errors='ignore')
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.plot(data['year'], data['life_expect'])
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('Life Expectancy')
    plt.title('What is the trend of life expectancy over time?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data.groupby('country')['pop'].sum().plot(kind='bar')
    plt.xlabel('Country')
    plt.ylabel('Population')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of population across different countries?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
        plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.hist(data['fertility'], bins=20)
    plt.xlabel('Fertility')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of fertility across different countries?', wrap=True)
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    box_plot_data = data.groupby('cluster')['life_expect'].apply(list)
    plt.boxplot(box_plot_data, labels=box_plot_data.index)
    plt.xlabel('Cluster')
    plt.ylabel('Life Expectancy')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of life expectancy across different clusters?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
